text: Josée Charbonneau (born 8 June 1972) is a Canadian freestyle skier. She was born in Val-David, Quebec. She competed at the 1998 Winter Olympics, in women's moguls. == References == == External links == * Category:1972 births Category:Sportspeople from Quebec Category:Living people Category:Canadian female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Canada Category:Freestyle skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Laurentides
